name: Sabina Karlsson (biracial model)
description:
Sabina Karlsson is a biracial 'plus-size' model. Father is Gambian and mother is Swedish. She's got a unique look and is unknown to SD, so I figured she'd be a good addition.

Trigger with 'skarl'. Warning: Her hair can not be contained. It yearns to be wild and free!

Trained for 31K+ steps on SD 1.5. Works well with Deliberate v2, hopefully others.
